data.description: FULLY RENOVATED CONDO WITH LAKE VIEWS IN ROCKWALL, TEXAS!! This 2 bed 2 bath condo is perfect for small families! The kitchen features granite counters, dual sinks, bar seating, stainless steel appliances, and access to the Utility closet. Washer, Dryer, and refrigerator will convey. The open layout hosts the dining room and living room offering ample space, a decorative fireplace, and mounted Flatscreen TV. The primary suite offers an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet. The second bedroom features a walk-in closet and ensuite bath. Step through the sliding barn door to the beautiful tiled covered patio. The HOA Covers water use and access to the 3 available pools in the Signal Ridge community. Within walking distance to the beautiful Rockwall Harbor offering ample shopping and dining experiences. Situated in the renowned Rockwall ISD. New HVAC in 2021 and a new water heater in 2023. YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS THIS!!
